### MinIO Setup

#### [NEW] [scripts/init-minio.sh](file:///c:/DEV/Tawjih%20V4/scripts/init-minio.sh)
Creates required buckets on first run: `tawjihi-audio`, `tawjihi-images`, `tawjihi-recordings`, `tawjihi-documents`.

